  "texts": [
    "To render the shadow, we add a very large plane under the car and enable the plane's Object Properties -Visibility -Mask -Shadow Catcher option.4.",
    "To obtain scene-related colored shadows, we construct the compositing node graph as Figure 14.",
    "This configuration generates the rendered image overlaid on the scene image, along with the accompanying depth information and mask of the vehicle and its corresponding shadow.",
    "The neighboring area division for vehicle placement.5.",
    "Using depth information and mask, we can handle the occlusion relationship with the original objects in the scene."
